---
---

<section class="bg-off-white py-8 lg:py-14">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center">

      <!-- Left: image -->
      <div class="lg:w-1/2 pt-6 lg:pt-0" data-reveal="left" data-reveal-mobile="off">
        <img
          src="/images/about-hand.jpg"
          alt="Técnico aplicando producto de detallado"
          width="600"
          height="450"
          class="w-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Right: text -->
      <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col gap-5" data-reveal="up" style="--reveal-delay: 100ms">
        <h2 class="text-text-dark font-bold leading-tight text-h1">
          The Duartes Standard.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm font-medium italic">
          More than just a service—it’s an automotive restoration experience.
        </p>
        <p class="text-black leading-relaxed">
          At Duartes Auto Detailing, we understand that your vehicle is a significant investment. That’s why, over the past three years, we’ve transformed more than 5,000 vehicles at over 1,000 locations throughout the Bay Area. We’re not a conventional car wash; we’re mobile specialists dedicated to taking your car’s appearance to the highest level.
        </p>

        <!-- Stats -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-200">
          <div
            data-reveal="up"
            style="--reveal-delay: 200ms"
            class="flex flex-col gap-1 text-center"
          >
            <span class="text-gold font-bold text-2xl">3+</span>
            <span class="text-text-muted text-xs leading-tight">Years of Experience</span>
          </div>
          <div
            data-reveal="up"
            style="--reveal-delay: 300ms"
            class="flex flex-col gap-1 text-center"
          >
            <span class="text-gold font-bold text-2xl">5,000+</span>
            <span class="text-text-muted text-xs leading-tight">Vehicles Detailled</span>
          </div>
          <div
            data-reveal="up"
            style="--reveal-delay: 400ms"
            class="flex flex-col gap-1 text-center"
          >
            <span class="text-gold font-bold text-2xl">1,000+</span>
            <span class="text-text-muted text-xs leading-tight">Locations in the Bay Area</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
